      <title>中国现金紧缩为外国人抢购银行债券带来福音</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/china-cash-crunch-a-boon-for-foreigners-snapping-up-bank-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在外资纷纷撤离中国债券市场的情况下，少数顽强的人选择坚持下去，利用有吸引力的利率将美元兑换成利润丰厚的短期银行债务交易策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/china-cash-crunch-a-boon-for-foreigners-snapping-up-bank-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
